{
  "text": "Abd-Rabou et al. (2010) reported that the acidity of Edam cheese fortifi ed by dietary zinc salts has been increased during the ripening in all the cheese samples. [CITATION_1] , also reported that the addition of zinc salts could increase the acidity.",
